<p>Hi <%= @resource.first_name %> <%= @resource.last_name %>,</p>

<p>Someone has requested a link to change your password, and you can do this using the following link:</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, :reset_password_token => @resource.reset_password_token) %></p>

<p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
<p>Your password won't change until you access the link above and set a new one.</p>
